{"tid":81980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做左餐飲業一年 你問我答","createTime":"2017-01-15T16:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T07:18:57.000Z","uid":65782,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07ee72f65e5ed2c9d376b9add99763443970dce2","tid":81980,"uid":65782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:07:34.000Z","msg":"做左一年話長唔長話短唔短<br />\n但就見盡做飲食既所有野<br />\n係廚房既黑暗史<br />\n香港人 大陸人 外國人既修養<br />\n奇怪客人既要求<br />\n<br />\n等我分享下今日先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日我比大陸人怒屌<br />\n原因係佢話自己聽唔明廣東話 屌9我要我用普通話同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我二話不說 調頭走左<br />\n心諗：你老味咁撚大個官威 我就再彩你都晒9氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好以為香港人好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實都一樣<br />\n做左咁耐 反而係賓妹最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53192e910e9abad436a73362b4f73a364ac2348e","tid":81980,"uid":15588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f13b5da0cd1205449069e695917e6cfd20d3063","tid":81980,"uid":65782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有咩趣事分享 <br />\n日日番工 啲客無腦好撚好笑<br />\n可以為番工既悶加啲樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb6976726d58ceeb5fea1f2eb5b13927863d884","tid":81980,"uid":69947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:15:38.000Z","msg":"我由pt開始都做左三年，<br />\n閪客見唔少，<br />\n大陸西係on9，但最on9一定係香港人"},{"pid":"bb055778d73c5a43d58c7c7589868369bbbb488b","tid":81980,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:19:49.000Z","msg":"其實叫我講普通話冇問題<br />\n但好多都係好無禮貌 一句「講普通話！」咁達埋黎 真係唔想serve你"},{"pid":"1895a7e